ДђГєng rб»“i вЂ” `new Bot(token)` khГґng cГі truyб»Ѓn `{ client: { fetch } }`, nГЄn grammY dГ№ng `node-fetch` mбє·c Д‘б»‹nh в†’ gГўy ETIMEDOUT trГЄn Node 20+.

**Fix:** ThГЄm native fetch vГ o Bot constructor:

```ts
this.bot = new Bot(this.telegramConfig.botToken, {
  client: { baseFetchConfig: { compress: true } },
});
```

Hoбє·c Д‘ЖЎn giбєЈn hЖЎn, truyб»Ѓn native fetch:

```ts
this.bot = new Bot(this.telegramConfig.botToken, {
  client: { fetch },
});
```

BбєЎn muб»‘n mГ¬nh fix luГґn khГґng? Hoбє·c nбєїu vбєҐn Д‘б»Ѓ lГ  mбєЎng (cбє§n VPN Д‘б»ѓ truy cбє­p Telegram API), thГ¬ fix code sбєЅ khГґng giГєp Д‘Ж°б»Јc.

